title: Bruning has an idea
view-if: sa_militarisation >= 0.5 and chancellor == 'Bruning' and sa_banned == 0
new-page: true
max-views: 1

- @ban_sa

@ban_sa
title: Chancellor Bruning is... banning the SA?
on-arrival: sa_banned == 1; sa_militarisation -= 0.5*interior_police_loyalty; sa_strength -= 100*interior_police_loyalty

In light of recent violence, Chancellor Bruning has decided to ban the ever-more militant SA. He may be an austritymaxxer, but at least he's not a Nazi.
